{"tid":1519730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[831購物日] 香港人 加油 支援香港商戶購物日","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:50:49.000Z","uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0953cb5df4ea0574b4a6e0b488a8fbcdf5cc2141","tid":1519730,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"香港7月零售市場慘淡<br />\n愛香港的香港人自然要為市場出一分力<br />\n解決因警暴同政暴問題導致的後果 幫依兩班廢物撿屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以831我地要多D進入不同店舖 唔買都睇下啦<br />\n咁買完野有禮貌地都同下個售貨員打下招呼 大叫我地香港人的口號 [光復香港 時代革命]<br />\n間中又叫下5大訴求 咁其實你只係自己一個/2個人行街買野<br />\n咁突然有其他人跟你講野 你控制唔到 <br />\n其實大家只係各自咁行街買野  咁岩講同一句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記住購物 購物 購物 為香港經濟出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce6c8edf9ed95132cbb5310c47f0ad110691a82","tid":1519730,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求入來推po！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士請快D碌入來！！！ 更新了整合名單，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1518567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cf9cf3bed27dddbc71cec3544054b045f2f3fb1d","tid":1519730,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance